1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:00:10,200 --> 00:00:11,320
This Li Qian

3
00:00:11,680 --> 00:00:12,680
is so sarcastic when she speaks.

4
00:00:12,800 --> 00:00:13,840
No one knows what she's thinking.

5
00:00:14,360 --> 00:00:14,840
She even caused

6
00:00:14,960 --> 00:00:15,920
such burden to us in work.

7
00:00:16,079 --> 00:00:17,080
That's a different matter.

8
00:00:17,240 --> 00:00:18,920
She donated the books with good intention.

9
00:00:19,080 --> 00:00:19,720
If you ask me,

10
00:00:19,840 --> 00:00:21,080
donating book is secondary.

11
00:00:21,240 --> 00:00:23,200
Her aim is to show off to us.

12
00:00:23,240 --> 00:00:24,000
I remember, today,

13
00:00:24,080 --> 00:00:25,040
you didn't do a lot of work either.

14
00:00:25,360 --> 00:00:26,640
The few remaining big boxes

15
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:28,120
were carried by me and Mr. Ai,

16
00:00:28,120 --> 00:00:29,280
right?

17
00:00:31,360 --> 00:00:32,400
True.

18
00:00:32,640 --> 00:00:34,000
Oh, right, Mr. Ai.

19
00:00:34,240 --> 00:00:35,960
You're the hero of the day.

20
00:00:36,200 --> 00:00:37,040
Wan Xia,

21
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:38,520
so,

22
00:00:39,080 --> 00:00:40,000
my husband is here to pick me up.

23
00:00:40,160 --> 00:00:41,000
I'll get going.

24
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:42,840
You two,

25
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:44,000
good luck.

26
00:00:44,040 --> 00:00:44,600
Goodbye.

27
00:00:45,520 --> 00:00:46,040
Let's go.

28
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:53,400
Zeng Li,

29
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:56,120
today, it seems

30
00:00:56,480 --> 00:00:58,000
you've been avoiding me.

31
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:03,160
[Why didn't I realize before]

32
00:01:03,680 --> 00:01:05,440
[that his mouth shape is so nice?]

33
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:10,680
[-They seem soft.]
-Zeng Li,

34
00:01:11,320 --> 00:01:12,400
[It's more than that.]

35
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:13,760
[They're indeed quite soft.]

36
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:14,600
Zeng Li!

37
00:01:14,800 --> 00:01:15,560
Zeng Li!

38
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:19,440
Must be my imagination.

39
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,320
We had an appointment this afternoon

40
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:23,520
to clean braces.

41
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:25,520
You also stood me up at the last minute.

42
00:01:25,640 --> 00:01:27,160
[Zeng Li, what are you trying to do?]

43
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:28,840
[Don't tell me you're thinking
to force your lips on him?]

44
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:30,880
[You hooligan.]

45
00:01:31,160 --> 00:01:32,640
Don't you have to work today?

46
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:34,720
I forgot to tell you

47
00:01:34,960 --> 00:01:36,160
when I made the appointment.

48
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,479
Is there something on my mouth?

49
00:01:46,320 --> 00:01:47,240
No.

50
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:50,240
I just feel that they're nice.

51
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:51,960
You can work as a lipstick model.

52
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:56,000
[I really admire myself.]

53
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,600
[Why am I saying
all these sensible stuff?]

54
00:01:59,320 --> 00:02:00,840
The weather's quite nice.

55
00:02:01,080 --> 00:02:03,000
Why don't we take a walk?

56
00:02:04,320 --> 00:02:06,680
So, what did Aunt say?

57
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,240
My mother said,

58
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:10,680
lazy people like me

59
00:02:10,919 --> 00:02:11,920
will never amount to anything.

60
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,800
Working as a librarian,

61
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:17,040
probably few more years later,
I'll be too embarrassed

62
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:18,400
to attend high school reunion party.

63
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,680
But,

64
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:23,840
that's how I am

65
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:24,640
as a person.

66
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:27,160
I dislike complicated
interpersonal relationships

67
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,600
and reading books is my hobby.

68
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:30,520
When I have time to spare,

69
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:32,240
I'll eat and drink with my good friends.

70
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,240
It makes us happy.

71
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:47,160
Could Mr. Ai look down on me

72
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:48,440
because I'm lazy?

73
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:51,120
Liu Yu Cheng once mentioned

74
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:53,440
you follow your daily routine strictly.

75
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:57,040
Work, studies, gym,

76
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:57,960
reading books,

77
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,720
everyday without fail.

78
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:03,000
He exaggerated.

79
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:05,560
I also often use my time

80
00:03:05,720 --> 00:03:06,640
to go to gym and study

81
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:07,640
to take a walk

82
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:08,600
and chat with you.

83
00:03:09,880 --> 00:03:10,680
I feel guilty.

84
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:12,920
I seem to have influenced the

85
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:14,200
respectable Mr. Ai in a negative manner.

86
00:03:16,760 --> 00:03:17,360
Well, I don't think

87
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:18,320
it's a bad thing.

88
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:21,560
On the contrary, I think
you're quite amazing.

89
00:03:23,760 --> 00:03:25,040
Are you trying to make me feel better?

90
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,200
Really.

91
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:27,480
You

92
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:29,480
aren't influenced by how others view you,

93
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:30,200
nor

94
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,480
let your family decide what you'll do.

95
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,960
You chose a job that you like

96
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:35,160
as well as lifestyle,

97
00:03:35,640 --> 00:03:36,720
that in itself is a

98
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,200
terrific achievement.

99
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:42,800
I'm not as good as you say.

100
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:44,120
If I really

101
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:45,520
have no self-doubt,

102
00:03:45,920 --> 00:03:46,920
just now,

103
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:49,040
I wouldn't be so upset.

104
00:03:49,920 --> 00:03:50,840
It's normal.

105
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:52,040
I also often

106
00:03:52,320 --> 00:03:54,079
have moments of self-doubt,

107
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:56,720
but making choices usually represent

108
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:57,520
your own attitude.

109
00:03:58,600 --> 00:03:59,520
Take me for example,

110
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:03,040
I seem to have chosen

111
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:05,920
a path which others regard
of as relatively successful,

112
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:08,040
but in fact I've given up

113
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:10,120
what I wanted to do a long time ago.

114
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:16,040
Mr. Ai, what is it

115
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:16,720
you wanted to do the most?

116
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:19,480
Have a guess.

117
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,240
Scientist?

118
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:27,800
Entrepreneur?

119
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:29,640
No,

120
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:30,600
these are

121
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,880
what's defined as really
successful people.

122
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:34,200
If it has to be an ambition that's unique

123
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:36,240
and niche...

124
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:40,520
A rockstar?

125
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:44,560
More or less.

126
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:47,360
I wanted to be a manga artist.

127
00:04:48,280 --> 00:04:48,960
Mr. Ai,

128
00:04:49,159 --> 00:04:49,840
that's a stark contrast

129
00:04:49,840 --> 00:04:51,000
with your current profession.

130
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:54,000
When I was younger, I saw

131
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,200
the male classmates in my class

132
00:04:55,760 --> 00:04:56,520
read manga often.

133
00:04:56,760 --> 00:04:57,760
I also enjoyed reading it.

134
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,000
I wanted to join them,

135
00:05:00,880 --> 00:05:01,640
but they thought

136
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:02,520
I was strange.

137
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:04,520
How can the first place in our grade

138
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:05,640
like to

139
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:06,520
read manga?

140
00:05:07,960 --> 00:05:09,000
When my grandmother heard of it,

141
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:10,400
she also prohibited me from doing so,

142
00:05:11,320 --> 00:05:12,600
saying it'll affect my studies.

143
00:05:13,840 --> 00:05:15,040
Since then,

144
00:05:16,080 --> 00:05:17,080
I'd wait until they fell asleep

145
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,400
to read in secret.

146
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:21,560
Although when I become older,

147
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:22,720
I'm free to do what I want,

148
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:25,640
but I've always kept this habit.

149
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,840
Following a strict routine

150
00:05:30,080 --> 00:05:32,240
is also my habit since young.

151
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:36,440
It's all for the 60 minutes
with most freedom

152
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:38,200
before sleep.

153
00:05:41,640 --> 00:05:42,520
Seems like Mr. Ai

154
00:05:42,520 --> 00:05:44,040
also grew up

155
00:05:44,159 --> 00:05:45,360
like any other usual male.

156
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:48,640
If I think of it this way, you seem

157
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,200
much more approachable.

158
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:53,040
Which is why,

159
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:54,920
you have to stick to

160
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:56,120
what you want to do.

161
00:05:56,960 --> 00:05:57,800
You have my support.

162
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:15,760
Actually,

163
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:19,120
your mouth shape is also very nice.

164
00:06:28,500 --> 00:06:33,740
[Sweet Teeth]
[Episode 11]

165
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:40,800
How are things going on between
you and your older girlfriend?

166
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:41,800
What did you mean?

167
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,120
Don't call her that.

168
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,840
She seems to be quite busy lately.

169
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:47,280
She hasn't been talking to me often

170
00:06:48,320 --> 00:06:49,960
and didn't respond when
I ask her to play game.

171
00:06:51,280 --> 00:06:53,000
Weren't you really close not long ago?

172
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,520
Since when has it become this way?

173
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,440
It's that night

174
00:06:56,520 --> 00:06:57,560
of our winning streak under my lead.

175
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:58,560
I suggest you

176
00:06:58,560 --> 00:06:59,960
to download Camps of Kings.

177
00:07:00,640 --> 00:07:01,400
Hurry.

178
00:07:01,700 --> 00:07:05,900
[Wu Ying]

179
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:05,920
She

180
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:09,360
came to check my battle result last night.

181
00:07:10,440 --> 00:07:11,640
32 visit counts,

182
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:13,320
but only 12 headcounts are recorded.

183
00:07:13,520 --> 00:07:14,800
Do you know what it means?

184
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:17,480
What?

185
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,280
You fool.

186
00:07:18,280 --> 00:07:19,720
She alone at least visited your account

187
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:20,720
20 times.

188
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:24,520
That means she cares about me.

189
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:26,640
So why is she ignoring me?

190
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:27,800
She's jealous.

191
00:07:28,080 --> 00:07:29,000
She thinks you and Xia Xia

192
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,280
play online game with each other everyday

193
00:07:30,440 --> 00:07:31,560
and fell out of love with her.

194
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:34,000
Your profile picture is Xia Xia?

195
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:35,120
You just realized?

196
00:07:35,440 --> 00:07:36,440
I didn't notice.

197
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:37,440
I thought it's just an
image you found online.

198
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:39,200
I've been using for a long time.

199
00:07:39,440 --> 00:07:40,600
Ever since I changed my profile picture

200
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:41,800
and switched the gender to female,

201
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:43,960
it became so much easier
to find someone to lead.

202
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:46,440
Where are you going?

203
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,680
I'm going to explain to her.

204
00:07:47,760 --> 00:07:48,400
No.

205
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:49,240
There's no rush.

206
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:50,520
Let's play another round.

207
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:51,920
Come on.

208
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:53,000
Father will be fine.

209
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:55,000
The door is open.

210
00:07:55,080 --> 00:07:55,640
They're here.

211
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:57,840
Father!

212
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,840
Dr. Jiang, how's my father?

213
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:02,920
The surgery is a success.

214
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:03,800
Don't worry.

215
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:04,520
It's just that, your father

216
00:08:04,520 --> 00:08:05,680
had an old injury on his leg.

217
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:06,880
This time, he fell

218
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:08,000
on the same spot as well.

219
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:09,560
When he moves,

220
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,840
it'll affect him more or less.

221
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:12,000
Doctor,

222
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:13,600
so from now on, is my husband

223
00:08:13,880 --> 00:08:14,720
going to sit on

224
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:15,520
a wheelchair?

225
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:16,520
Aunt, it's not to that extent.

226
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,360
Don't worry.

227
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,760
His movements will be a bit slow.

228
00:08:18,880 --> 00:08:20,520
It's best to have someone look after him.

229
00:08:20,640 --> 00:08:22,000
OK, sure. Thank you, Doctor.

230
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:22,640
No problem.

231
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:23,560
Slowly.

232
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:24,320
Come on.

233
00:08:24,520 --> 00:08:25,720
Mother, you all go ahead.

234
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:26,280
I'll catch up with you.

235
00:08:26,640 --> 00:08:27,000
OK.

236
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:28,720
-Careful.
-Careful.

237
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:32,640
Thank you, Dr. Jiang.

238
00:08:32,919 --> 00:08:33,919
I'm just doing my part.

239
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:35,240
To me, in each surgery,

240
00:08:35,280 --> 00:08:36,400
I'll do my best,

241
00:08:36,799 --> 00:08:37,679
but this time,

242
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,120
I really hope

243
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:40,520
I'll perform better than usual.

244
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:49,520
Don't you remember me?

245
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:51,160
You're my father's surgeon.

246
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:51,760
Didn't we already

247
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:52,960
meet few times before this?

248
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:53,920
The first time we met,

249
00:08:54,160 --> 00:08:55,680
was at the first meeting

250
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:56,800
since my transfer to
Donghu University Hospital.

251
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:58,440
You were sitting right next to me.

252
00:08:58,680 --> 00:09:00,040
At that time, the principal
and vice principal

253
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:01,160
took turns to speak.

254
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,240
You were holding a tablet

255
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,200
without lifting your head once.

256
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,480
I guess you were writing a thesis.

257
00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:09,080
And I thought

258
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:12,240
this female's quite bold,

259
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:13,800
but she looks cool.

260
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:15,440
The weekly hospital meetings

261
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,320
is the time I'm most efficient

262
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:17,440
at writing theses.

263
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:18,800
I understand.

264
00:09:19,800 --> 00:09:20,800
Six shifts a week,

265
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,440
at least nine hours each.

266
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:23,520
Patients' monthly medical records

267
00:09:23,520 --> 00:09:24,760
have to be compiled into a report as well.

268
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:25,560
Each year, you also need to

269
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:26,600
publish at least four theses

270
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:27,800
on academic journals.

271
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:30,800
The path to become attending physician

272
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:32,440
sure isn't easy.

273
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:35,640
Good luck.

274
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,280
I already passed my tests

275
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:38,360
and the interview.

276
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:39,760
As for when a spot

277
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:40,640
is available,

278
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:41,440
I can only wait

279
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,840
for instructions from
hospital's management.

280
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:46,440
You can do it.

281
00:09:47,560 --> 00:09:48,200
Thank you.

282
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:49,800
The lift is here.

283
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:50,840
Let's go.

284
00:09:59,460 --> 00:10:04,020
[and Liu Yu Cheng, two players mode]

285
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:01,720
[This rascal]

286
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:03,000
[is still playing with Xia Xia.]

287
00:10:03,640 --> 00:10:05,360
Dr. Wu, are you available this weekend?

288
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:07,680
Dr. Wu.

289
00:10:10,040 --> 00:10:11,240
What were you saying?

290
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:12,280
I said,

291
00:10:12,280 --> 00:10:13,640
